## PRACTICAL LAB — Two-Container Network

```powershell
docker network create app-net
docker run -d --name redis --network app-net redis:alpine
docker run -it --rm --network app-net alpine ping -c 3 redis
docker network rm app-net
docker rm -f redis
```

